API - GET /categories
This can be used to list all the available categories and the number of items available on that category.

API - GET /categories/:categoryName
This API can be used to list the products available in that particular category

API - GET /products
This API can be used to list all the products available

API - GET /products/:productId
This API can be used to find that particular product details

API - GET /setup
This API can be used to setup the db with the initial data.


To run the application

    1. Execute 'npm update' from the root of the application
    2. Configure .env file in root with Database connection details and port number
    3. Execute 'npm start' to start the application

API tools like Postman can be used to consume/test the API.